Bolívar : Barú, Cartagena de Indias (Caribbean) (
Carpio-Díaz et al. 2016
).

Widely distributed in Atlantic coastal areas of Mexico ( Kensley & Schotte 1989 ); Florida, Cuba ( Van Name 1936 ); Bahamas , Tobago , Bonaire ( Schultz 1974 ); Dominica , Curacao , Virgin Islands , Belize , Venezuela ( Kensley & Schotte 1989 ); Puerto Rico (
Hurtado et al. 2014
); Colombia (
Carpio-Díaz et al. 2016
); and Brazil ( Silva & Alves 2000 ). It is also present on the Pacific coast of Costa Rica (
Taiti et al. 2018
). First record of the species for continental islands of the Colombian Caribbean.
